brewery.brewery_description:
WELCOME TO FUTURE BREWING!

We are an independent microbrewery in St Peters, Sydney. Our focus is on quality beer using forward thinking brewing techniques, creating balance and flavour in every beer we brew. Future Brewing aims to push the boundaries of modern brewing while respecting the methods of the past.

beer.beer_description: We teamed up with Freestyle Hops to design this single hop DDH Hazy DIPA dry hopped entirely with Nelson Sauvin. Using mid harvest, late harvest and SubZero Hop Kief it creates a complex flavour and aroma profile. Skin contact savvy b, passion fruit & guava alongside some dank, grapefruit & tropical fruit.
This Hazy IPA is double dry hopped with Mosaic, Mosaic Cryo and Nelson. Tropical and dank! Just how we like it!

beer.beer_description:
Our First Hazy DIPA!!!
This DDH Hazy DIPA is layered with absurd amounts of Citra, Mosaic & Nelson. Sweet Citrus and Tropical Fruit.
TDH Hazy TIPA dry hopped with 3 different lots of Nelson from 2 different hop farms. Bright citrus, juicy stonefruit, sweet tropical and a kiss of NZ dank.
This decadent pastry stout is loaded with insane amounts of coconut and a touch of nilla. Liquid bounty bar!!!
A pillowy, hazy, double dry hopped IPA Brewed in collaboration with Track Brewing Co. Nelson, Nelson SubZero Hop Kief, Nectaron & HBC586. Passion fruit, stone fruit, citrus.
West Coast Double IPA double dry hopped with Mosaic, Motueka, HBC586 & Nelson. Tropical, dank, piney.
Imperial Stout loaded with insane amounts of roasted hazelnuts, cocoa nibs and vanilla. Thic and lush with notes of milk chocolate, oily hazelnuts and vanilla wafers. Nutella in a glass!

This DDH Hazy IPA was brewed with wheat and oats and double dry hopped with Citra, Citra Cryo & Riwaka. It’s got a big creamy body with flavours and aromas of juicy exotic citrus and intense tropical fruit.

This Cali IPA was brewed with 100% extra pale malt and given the double dry hop treatment with Citra, Mosaic, Nelson and Kohia Nelson SubZero Hop Kief. Dank and resinous with blueberry, white wine and passion fruit.
Hazy West Coast IPA with Citra and Motueka. Juicy tropical fruit and lemon/lime. Yum!
DDH Hazy Pale with punchy Eggers Riwaka, citrusy Freestyle Motueka and Motueka SubZero HopKief.
This juicy pale is double dry hopped with our hand selected Freestyle Nelson. Bright and citrusy - Papaya, Red Grapefruit and Nectarine.
Brewed in collaboration with our best buds from Alvarado Street Brewery. DDH West Coast IPA with Mosaic, Nectaron and Krush. Notes of dank blueberry and sticky pineapple.
DDH Hazy Pale with Nelson and Motueka. Soft and lush body with notes of fresh citrus and juicy stonefruit.
DDH Hazy Pale with Citra, Mosaic and Moteuka SubZero HopKief. Our most tropical and citrus forward pale yet!

Modern IPA with 100% Freestyle Riwaka. This lands somewhere between East and West Coast IPA styles. 
Notes of exotic citrus and dank tropical fruit (papaya and gummy candy).
This crushable little hazy pale is double dry hopped with Motueka, Rakau and Kohia Nelson SubZero Hop Kief. Crushed citrus, ripe stonefruit & passionfruit juice.
Soft and juicy pale packed with some of our most loved NZ hops. White wine, passion fruit and mojito vibes.
